There are 4 classes. 

Interface.java - This is the graphical user interface for the robot controls. 

Hardware.java - This is the robot hardware design on the panel2 of Interface. 

TechServ.java - This is the technical services layer of the robot. It will contain all the action Listeners. 

ImgFrame.java - This is the camera layer of the robot. It will be invoked when the camera of the robot is turned on. 

Everything is functioning as per the requirements. 

Thank you. 
